【例 20.8】设二元函数  F(\xi, \eta)  的两个偏导数  F_{1}^{\prime}, F_{2}^{\prime}  不同时为零,  u(x, y)  具有二阶连续偏导数且 满足  F\left(\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}, \frac{\partial u}{\partial y}\right)=0 , 证明:\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}\right)^{2}【解析】运用函数偏导数性质运算求得.

【答案】

 由  u(x, y)  具有二阶连续偏导数, 可知\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}=\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y \partial x} \text {. }

 将  F\left(\frac{\partial u}{\partial x}, \frac{\partial u}{\partial y}\right)=0  两端分别关于  x, y  求偏导数, 可得 F_{1}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}}+F_{2}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y \partial x}=0 , 

即  F_{1}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}}=-F_{2}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y \partial x} ; 

 F_{1}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}+F_{2}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}=0 ,

 即  F_{2}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}=-F_{1}^{\prime} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y} . (* *) 

从而可得  \quad F_{1}^{\prime} F_{2}^{\prime} \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}
=F_{1}^{\prime} F_{2}^{\prime} \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y \partial x} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}
=F_{1}^{\prime} F_{2}^{\prime}\left(\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}\right)^{2} .

 若  F_{1}^{\prime}, F_{2}^{\prime}  皆不为零, 则必有  \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}\right)^{2} .

 若  F_{1}^{\prime}=0  (或  \left.F_{2}^{\prime}=0\right) , 由 (*) 及  (* *)  式可知  \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y \partial x}=0=\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}\left(\right.  或  \left.\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}}=0=\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}\right) .从而也有  \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x^{2}} \cdot \frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial y^{2}}=\left(\frac{\partial^{2} u}{\partial x \partial y}\right)^{2} .

【综上所述，答案为\frac{\sqrt{6}}{12}\pi】

